task.summary: Drawing line works even with overlapping lines, there is an issue with the stat panel not being repainted properly. - Might add a devInfoPanel to show details of what is going on and display things like overlapping lines, vertecies and other useful information. - I thought injecting everything though set methods would be more readable instead of using contructor but it didnt, I think I will change that. - Now working on creating polygons by drawing lines that intersect, if two or more lines are connected but not closed off, then they will form a connected line object, if they are closed of they will form a polygon object. If a line passes twice through the same connected line object, it will form a polygon, if it passes through a polygon then it will form 2 new polygons from the old one.
